# ai-stack .gitignore
#
# This tree mixes symlinks (read-only views) with our own content.
# We commit the .md / .yaml we author, and we DON'T follow symlinks into
# the live data dirs (those have their own .gitignore in their home).

# Symlinked dirs (live data, versioned elsewhere)
04-reference/
05-artifacts/cron-output/live
05-artifacts/kanban/live

# Symlinked config (we author ROUTING.yaml alongside these, no need to track both)
02-routing/hermes-config.yaml
02-routing/cron-jobs.json

# Working artifacts — versioned manually, not in this git repo
05-artifacts/work/*
!05-artifacts/work/.gitkeep

# Logs
*.log
*.log.*
*.jsonl
.errors.log

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.tmp
